  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Impact on outcome of early endoscopic extraction of bile duct stones in biliary pancreatitis:
      a prospective multicenter randomized controlled study.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Impact on outcome of early endoscopic extraction of bile duct stones in biliary pancreatitis:
      a prospective multicenter randomized controlled study.

      Main objective: to test the interest of early bile duct decompression by endoscopic
      sphincterotomy after early non invasive diagnosis by endosonography or MR cholangiography.

      Prospective multicenter randomized controlled study with direct patient benefit
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
